%N A180713 If n is even then a(n) = 3n, if n == 1 mod 4 then a(n) = 3n+1, if n == 3 mod 4 then a(n) = 3n+2.
%H A180713 Vincenzo Librandi, <a href="/A180713/b180713.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..1000</a>
